high_descs: TUrn left and walk across the room to face the sink.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Turn around and step forward to face the lettuce on the counter.
Cut the lettuce on the counter into slices.
Turn around and step forward to face the counter.
Place the knife on the counter.
Turn around and step forward to face the lettuce on the counter.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the counter.
Turn around and step forward to face the fridge.
Cool the lettuce slice in the fridge and remove it.
Take a step to the left to face the counter.
Place the lettuce slice on the counter to the right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To cool a lettuce slice and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Go to the sink
Pick up the knife from the sink
Turn around and go to the kitchen counter in the middle of the room
Cut the cabbage on the counter into slices
Turn around and go to the coffee maker
Place the knife vertically in front of the coffee maker
Go back to the counter with the sliced cabbage
Pick up a slice of cabbage from the counter
Go to the fridge
Open the fridge, put the cabbage slice in the top left tray, close the fridge, wait for a few seconds, open the fridge, take the slice out, and close the fridge
Turn to your left and go to the coffee maker
Place the cabbage slice on the counter in front of the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled slice of cabbage on the counter

high_descs: Turn left, go forward, turn left, go forward, turn right and go to the sink
Pick up the knife in the sink
Turn around, go to the counter
Slice the lettuce on the counter
Turn around, go to the counter
Put the knife on the counter
Turn around, go to the counter
Pick up a lettuce slice from counter
Turn right, go forward, turn left a the the fridge
Put the lettuce slice in the fridge, wait, pick up the lettuce slice from the fridge
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the counter
Put the lettuce slice on the counter
anns.task_desc: Slice a lettuce and cool a slice
